{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a9fc191f08","title":"对陕北公学第十一至第二十队学员的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ddf51eeeca","index":0,"year":1938,"month":3,"day":29,"articleId":"a9fc191f08"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fdfb139074","type":"paragraph","text":"对陕北公学第十一至第二十队学员","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"a9fc191f08"},{"id":"fed482ad62","type":"paragraph","text":"的讲话","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"a9fc191f08"},{"id":"c5370be459","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年3月29日）有了人民、国民党和共产党的进步这三个条件，中国不会亡国。有人说地方太小了，好的地方已被敌人占去，即使抵抗也不行。然而我是项固党的最后胜利派，仍旧主张我们会胜利。王义之说“大块假我以文章”，昌只大地方可以做文章吗？小块也行。有人说中国亡了，我说不会亡，城市亡了，乡村未亡：大路亡了，小路未亡：白天亡了，夜里未亡。抗战不仅需要大大发展共产党，而且需要非党布尔什维克，例如鲁迅就是非党布尔什维克部分。[1]这是毛泽东第五次到陕北公学，对第十一至第二十队学员讲语的一","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"a9fc191f08"}],"page":{"id":"3b750c6f9a","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"a9fc191f08","start":125,"end":125}}}},"__N_SSG":true}